nodes.text: Dorrick was a male Human Mandalorian residing in the Outpost Rennar on the planet Tatooine during the Cold War. He wore blue Mandalorian armor. When the Tusken Raider chief, Bloodgouge had made plans to destroy Outpost Rennar, Dorrick and Gezda offered Imperial spacers a chance take him out.
Dorrick is a non-player character from the massively multi-player online role playing game Star Wars: The Old Republic released by BioWare in 2011. He is voiced by Nolan North.
